                <div class="copytext">
                  
    <div id="switchableCopyText" data-js-switchable-content='["previewText","fullText"]'>
      <div id="previewText" class="preview-text"><div class="markdown-it"><p>The painting shows the personification of Justice as a half-length figure against a dark background, holding her attributes: the sword and the scales. She wears her hair pinned up under a decorative snood and a gauzy veil falls over her face to just above the eyes. A tunic of similar</p>
</div></div>
      <div class="is-cut full-text" id="fullText"><div class="markdown-it"><p>The painting shows the personification of Justice as a half-length figure against a dark background, holding her attributes: the sword and the scales. She wears her hair pinned up under a decorative snood and a gauzy veil falls over her face to just above the eyes. A tunic of similar material covers her naked body without concealing it. Her attire is completed by a choker and a linked chain with a pendant wrapped twice around her neck.</p>
<p>[cda 2020]</p>
</div></div>
    </div>
    
                </div>
